Description: African Red Slip Ware wheel-made pottery vessel rim sherd. Light orange fabric.
Curator's comments: African Red Slip tableware sherd .Thin red wash and eroded, but resembles in fabric and form ARS form 80A (Hayes 1972, 126-8). Hayes, J.W. 1972. Late Roman Pottery. London.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (IF.090) (Phase 3)
